---
description: Shared shell, layout, and public-surface guidance
globs:
  - "src/app/**"
  - "src/components/**"
  - "src/features/home/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Preserve the current visual language and shared shell unless the task is explicitly design-led.
- Prefer server components by default; add `"use client"` only when required.
- Keep app-wide providers in `src/components/providers` and shared chrome in `src/components/shared`.
- Do not move feature-specific logic into shared components.
